&lt;p&gt;Trello is quickly becoming one of my favorite tools of all time. Who would&amp;rsquo;ve thought that a list of lists could be so useful? Fog Creek, I guess!&amp;#160;&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-backref&#34; role=&#34;doc-backlink&#34;&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
