&lt;p&gt;I revel in the possibility of that guy having thought to himself, &amp;ldquo;I gotta remember to bring my Michael Jackson glove to the game!&amp;rdquo;&amp;#160;&lt;a href=&#34;#fnref:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-backref&#34; role=&#34;doc-backlink&#34;&gt;&amp;#x21a9;&amp;#xfe0e;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
