      &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://necro-skeletal.deviantart.com/art/Pixel-Heart-332654763&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://jerodsanto.net/drop/pixel-heart-by-necro-skeletal.png&#34; alt=&#34;via Necro-Skeletal on Deviant Art&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
